<template>
  <v-container fluid>
    <v-row class="my-2">
      <v-col md="4">
        <v-card>
          <v-card-text>
              <v-virtual-scroll
                :bench="benched"
                :items="items"
                height="100%"
                item-height="64"
              >
              </v-virtual-scroll>
          </v-card-text>
        </v-card>
      </v-col>
      <v-col>
        <v-card>
          <v-card-text>
          sd
          </v-card-text>
        </v-card>
      </v-col>

<script>
  export default {
    data: () => ({
      benched: 0,
    }),
    computed: {
      items () {
        return Array.from({ length: this.length }, (k, v) => v + 1)
      },
      length () {
        return 7000
      },
    },
  }
</script>
